I"<h3 id="py-auto-gui">py auto gui</h3>

<p>as p</p>

<p><em>설정 - 보안 및 개인 정보 보호 - 개인정보보호 - 손쉬운 사용 - 터미널 체크</em></p>

<p>마우스와 키보드를 제어한다. &gt; 자동화 프로그램 ( 매크로 ) 생성 시 이용</p>

<p>마우스 좌표를 먼저 알아야 함 : 해상도에 따른 위치</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">position</span><span class="p">()</span>
<span class="c1"># (x, y)
</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">moveTo</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">y</span><span class="p">(,</span> <span class="n">time</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="c1"># 절대적인 위치 변경
</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">moveRel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">y</span><span class="p">(,</span> <span class="n">time</span><span class="p">))</span>
<span class="c1"># 상대적인 위치 변경
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="click">Click</h4>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">click</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="c1"># 한 번
</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">click</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">clicks</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">interval</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1"># 두 번 클릭, 클릭 사이에 2초 텀
</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">doubleClick</span><span class="p">()</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="keyboard-ctrl">Keyboard Ctrl</h4>

<p><strong>파일이 열리는 시간을 생각해서 typewrite 필수</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>‘키’를 누를 때는 [대괄호] 내에 삽입</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">time</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">sleep</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="c1"># 1초 쉼
</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">typewrite</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Hello'</span><span class="p">)</span> 
<span class="n">p</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">typewrite</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="s">'enter'</span><span class="p">])</span> 
</code></pre></div></div>

